$$
\psi\circ\varphi^{-1}\colon\varphi(U\cap V)\to\psi(U\cap V)
$$

is a [[homeomorphism|Hom√∂omorphismus]] between open sets of $$\R^m$$ and is called a //change of coordinates// or //transition function.//

